**Statement:**

```
Any particle with m > 0 (P_im = mc ≠ 0)
cannot reach the null geodesic (d² = 0)
while remaining a particle.

The only physical transitions across the null geodesic are:

(a) Annihilation: matter + antimatter → photons
    [counterclockwise + clockwise oscillator = cancellation]

(b) Bounce: Pauli floor compression → new cycle
